Message: The user completes the submission of the form
Hello, my ad has been pending for almost a week but I thought it should only take 1-2 days to be approved or rejected. How can I speed up the process?

Hi Brian, I'm sorry to hear that your ad has been pending for so long. Typically, the ad approval process takes between 1-2 business days. Since it's been almost a week, it might be due to an issue with account verification. To speed up the process, please provide the following details by emailing adsupport@newsbreak.com with the subject line: Business Verification –
- Company's full address
- Company's legal entity name
- Company's EHID or DUNS number
- Primary contact person's name
- Company's phone number
Once we receive this information, we will conduct a thorough review and update you on your account status.
We appreciate your cooperation in maintaining a secure and compliant advertising environment for all our partners.
Bgs Giftshop 3212 E Granada rd Phoenix AZ 85008 277860518 Brian Green 216.496.7736

Thanks, Brian! I've sent your information to our support team. They will review it and update you on your account status soon. If you have any other questions or need further assistance, feel free to ask!
You're welcome, Brian! If you need any more help, just let me know. Have a great day!
